first word should always be the query ( word | words )

if there query has a <space> char in between :
    use <doublequote>s to wrap the query words

flags :
    there are 2 types of flags 
    valued flags : -f=value 
        if the value has <space> in between you can again use <doublequote>s  
    bool flags : -f

exmaple : "colum bus" -d -dir=zynger69

